What to do to configure debian the way I like

Add thales	ALL=(ALL:ALL) ALL to /etc/sudoers

Add shortcut Ctrl Alt T to xfce4-terminal (Settings -> Keyboard)

Install (command line programs):
git
vim
zsh
oh-my-zsh 
pathogen
nerdtree
ctrlp
tmux (Edit -> Preferences -> Run custom command ...: tmux)
oh-my-tmux 

Install (other programs):
synapse (run with startup)
paraview
spyder
wps-office
texmaker
chrome to linux
dropbox
